results.name: War of Genesis - 起源战争
results.description: 1.背景：在人类起源之前，流传着这样一个传说，世上有人族和异族两大种族，双方为了自己种族的生存和发展
results.fullDescription: 1.背景：在人类起源之前，流传着这样一个传说，世上有人族和异族两大种族，双方为了自己种族的生存和发展，争夺星球的控制权，双方开展了史诗般的战争。 2.玩法：在游戏中玩家将在人族和异族两大阵营中选择一个阵营加入，两个种族将不定期进行战役。玩家可以选择直接参加战斗，战斗形式多样，可以1V1也可以组队团战，玩家可根据自己的喜好搭配不同兵种，排兵布阵，进行战斗。玩家也可以选择不直接参战，而是赞助战场上的任何一方，获胜后将按赞助占比获得奖励。 3.区块链：所有玩家的物品将记录在区块链上，可以永久访问和使用，战斗及奖励规则等都将由智能合约控制，对于所有玩家来说都是公开透明的。 Before the origin of mankind, there was a legend that there were two races in the world, one being human, another being aliens. Both sides competed for the control of the planet for the survival and development of their own races, thus an epic war between the two began. In the game, the player will choose one of the two camps of Human and Alien, and battles will take place between the two camps from time to time. Players can choose to participate in the battle directly. The battles are various in form. They can be 1 vs 1 or in groups. There are multiple arms in the game that allows players to match different arms according to their own preferences and arrange for battles. Players can also choose not to participate directly in the battle, but to sponsor any party on the battlefield. After winning, they will be rewarded according to the proportion of their sponsorship.
